{"tid":2306631,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"狗拘43歲男子涉上周在深水埗一間地鋪偷貓","createTime":"2020-11-30T14:35:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T15:48:43.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f4de529759155d1a7ba92569cb6787081cc094b8","tid":2306631,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T14:35:01.000Z","msg":"警拘43歲男子涉上周在深水埗偷貓<br />\n<br />\n警方拘捕一名43歲男子，涉嫌上星期在深水埗偷去一隻約3個月大貓隻。警方表示，上周五早上接到荔枝角道一間地鋪東主報案，指飼養的貓隻在店鋪門外被偷走。警方翻查閉路電視後，鎖定疑犯身份，下午在大角咀洋松街一個大廈單位將他拘捕，初步懷疑他路過店鋪時覺得貓隻可愛，想抱回家飼養。<br />\n<br />\n貓隻經初步檢查後證實健康良好，晚上已交回主人。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2368694\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2368694&d=AMq1wuZoRE%2BfxlTDVFm3xOIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=78d36f53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2368694</a>"},{"pid":"db5d3c814e2062451a28255b08cc64539e4263c7","tid":2306631,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T14:49:48.000Z","msg":"下次扔隻貓落街跌死佢啦<br />\n咁就乜事都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78f5e6c1d84143e66c637a25029fdeefcf36c353","tid":2306631,"uid":116705,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"db5d3c814e2062451a28255b08cc64539e4263c7","tid":2306631,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T14:49:48.000Z","msg":"下次扔隻貓落街跌死佢啦<br />\n咁就乜事都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T15:03:18.000Z","msg":"你老母都未扔你落街"},{"pid":"2ca901d798d1b994d1fcd1c4eb7c8aa7d2e86c0f","tid":2306631,"uid":124655,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T15:48:43.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇新聞好大陣仗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又黑布蒙頭又上晒手扣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 心諗咩事呀"}]}